These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
House: cottage, tower, townhouse
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, doctor, entrepreneur
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the cottage house is between the doctor and the entrepreneur##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the tower house##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| House         | tower | cottage   | townhouse   |
| Job   | doctor     | designer | entrepreneur |
| Sport   | snowboarding  | ice-hockey    | rugby      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, bartender, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, skateboard
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, almond-milk
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the bartender is the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the manager is the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the fan of gospel and the police-officer##2
6. the police-officer is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Job          | bartender  | manager     | police-officer     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Transport   | skateboard  | scooter | quad-bike |
| Beverage           | almond-milk | iced-tea     | mirinda       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, german, british
House: victorian, ranch-style, wooden
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard, van
1. the victorian house is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the wooden house and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the italian is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is the german##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality          | italian  | british     | german     |
| House           | wooden | victorian  | ranch-style   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Transport           | van     | helicopter | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, cola
House: gothic-revival, palace, wooden
3 different games are played: poker, go, monopoly
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the person drinking cola is between the palace house and the person playing poker##2
4. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate       | cola  | milk   |
| House     | palace    | wooden  | gothic-revival |
| Game     | go   | monopoly | poker        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

