.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, designer, firefighter
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily, iris
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, october, august
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is between the fan of gospel and the person who growsiris##2
3. the person who growsazalea is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the paramedic is on the right of the firefighter##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Job          | firefighter    | paramedic     | designer      |
| Flower         | azalea | lily | iris |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| Birthday           | october     | december       | august     |

