.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pumpkin
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, blue, lavender
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, milk
House: townhouse, ranch-style, wooden
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is the person who likes brown##1
3. the person drinking 7up is between the person eating pineapple and the ranch-style house##2
4. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | pumpkin    |
| Color         | blue | lavender      | brown |
| Beverage   | coffee   | 7up     | milk        |
| House           | townhouse      | wooden       | ranch-style      |

