.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, horse, mouse
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, skydiving
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, indonesian, nigerian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, january
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the russian##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the owner of the mouse and the person who's birthday is in february##2
3. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Pet          | mouse      | horse   | turtle |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | skydiving |
| Nationality   | russian      | nigerian | indonesian   |
| Birthday     | january         | august  | february       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different games are played: domino, bridge, backgammon
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, iris
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, march, november
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the architect is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person playing backgammon##2
5. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Game      | domino       | bridge      | backgammon      |
| Flower         | balloon-flower    | iris | bellflower      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Birthday   | march     | november          | june       |

