.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, ritmeester, cain
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, chess, skydiving
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, nigerian, russian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, classical, folk
1. the fan of folk is between the nigerian and the russian##2
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
5. the indian is on the left of the fan of classical##1
6. the fan of classical is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | siglo      | ritmeester | cain     |
| Hobby          | chess   | reading      | skydiving     |
| Nationality   | russian  | indian      | nigerian |
| Music-Genre     | trance | folk        | classical     |

