.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, corn, grapes
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, sailing
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, egyptian, australian
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking fanta and the person eating corn##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person eating grapes##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the australian is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the indonesian is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Food       | corn       | grapes       | potato    |
| Beverage         | mirinda | juice | fanta |
| Sport       | lacrosse      | sailing         | handball |
| Nationality   | indonesian        | australian            | egyptian  |

