.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, car, roller
There 3 different types of food: apple, plum, blueberry
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, october
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person driving the car and the person driving the scooter##2
5. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk     | hot-chocolate | coffee      |
| Transport         | car  | roller       | scooter |
| Food   | blueberry   | plum         | apple     |
| Birthday   | june | july    | october     |

