.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, chinchilla
There 3 different types of food: spinach, carrot, radish
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, skydiving, cooking
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, spanish
1. the owner of the horse is the person eating radish##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the horse is between the person eating carrot and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Pet      | dog | horse      | chinchilla            |
| Food           | spinach | radish | carrot |
| Hobby   | skydiving     | cooking        | sudoku         |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | australian    | spanish        |

