.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-13::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, nurse, pilot
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, rock-climbing, magic-tricks
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, siglo, davidoff
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, aquamarine, white
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the nurse is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the davidoff-smoker##2
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | architect | nurse        | pilot       |
| Hobby   | reading | rock-climbing | magic-tricks |
| Cigar           | davidoff     | siglo         | tiparillo  |
| Color         | aquamarine  | white       | mauve  |

