.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
3 different games are played: domino, whist, mah-jongg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dannemann, bluemaster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, golf, soccer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person watching disaster movies and the bluemaster-smoker##2
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person playing whist##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the blend-smoker is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Game      | whist    | mah-jongg          | domino |
| Cigar          | bluemaster | dannemann           | blend        |
| Sport           | golf | soccer | tennis         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

