.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-15::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, emerald, red
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, havana, oliveros
City: venice, san-francisco, hamburg
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the fan of trance and the oliveros-smoker##2
3. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes emerald is between the fan of trance and the person who likes turquise##2
5. the fan of punk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Color          | red  | emerald   | turquise |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | punk     | classical |
| Cigar   | game | havana | oliveros   |
| City     | hamburg   | san-francisco   | venice      |

