The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, september, may
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in december and the aristoff-smoker##2
3. the photographer is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the librarian##1
6. the librarian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Job       | photographer | librarian | journalist |
| Cigar         | aristoff   | bolivar       | fonseca        |
| Sport       | parkour | cricket   | golf         |
| Birthday   | may    | september     | december         |

