.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, cola
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, documentary, horror
3 different games are played: snooker, bridge, backgammon
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, ship, train
1. the person watching documentary movies is between the person driving the train and the person watching satire movies##2
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the person playing bridge##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee  | cola     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | documentary | satire |
| Game           | snooker        | backgammon   | bridge  |
| Transport     | train      | ship   | airplane |

