.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, domino
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, april, august
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, ship, trike
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, mouse
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
6. the person playing domino is between the person playing backgammon and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Game           | billiard   | domino   | backgammon |
| Birthday   | august | april   | january     |
| Transport   | ship     | boat      | trike    |
| Pet           | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse    |

