.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, oliveros, chaman
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, boat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, parkour, handball
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the bongani-smoker and the person driving the skateboard##2
4. the person who's sport is parkour is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the oliveros-smoker and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Cigar      | bongani | chaman     | oliveros        |
| Transport         | trike   | boat | skateboard |
| Sport   | parkour        | snowboarding       | handball      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

