.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
3 different games are played: poker, snooker, backgammon
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, teacher, musician
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, vegafina, bluemaster
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the teacher##1
2. the person playing snooker is the siglo-smoker##1
3. the teacher is the siglo-smoker##1
4. the coach is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person playing backgammon is between the bluemaster-smoker and the teacher##2
6. the musician is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Game         | snooker     | backgammon    | poker        |
| Job       | teacher | musician   | coach   |
| Cigar   | siglo          | vegafina     | bluemaster       |

 